  openingStory: The gem waits at the heart of the ruins behind every lesson the jungle
    has taught. Gassy Gorilla has a plan, which is mostly all of them.
  successStory: The shiny gem comes home as a family lantern. Gassy Gorilla requests
    that history record the landing from his best side.
  lessonText: Complete all five environmental skills in order, then reach the gem
    gate.
